Package com.sixbank.auditlogger.log

Class AuditLog

java.lang.Object
com.sixbank.auditlogger.log.AuditLog
public class AuditLog extends Object
AuditLog is the core structure for audit records. It is designed to be GDPR/KYC compliant and indexed into Elasticsearch.
